HEADWORD: Sugaring
<hw>Sug"ar*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of covering
or sweetening with sugar; also, the sugar thus used.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The act or process of making sugar.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sugarless</ent>⟦br⟧
